  "body": "<span class=\"VIiyi\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"ru\" data-phrase-index=\"0\" data-number-of-phrases=\"1\">Power Utilities - addon to IndustrialUpgrade. A feature of Power Utilities is that the mod allows you to convert energy from one type to another, and then back. This mod adds only one block - this is a converter from EU to RF, EU to FE and EU to TE&nbsp; and vice versa (Power Converter).<br></span></span>\n\n![Convertors](https://i.postimg.cc/zD6FTKQv/2022-02-08-00-05-51.png)\n\n<span class=\"VIiyi\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"ru\" data-phrase-index=\"0\" data-number-of-phrases=\"1\"><a href=\"https://i.postimg.cc/d1Fp2PZn/2022-02-08-00-01-47.png\"><img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/509p9xCc/2022-02-08-00-02-32.png\" alt=\"Module for crafting\"></a></span></span>",
